      "After calculating: verify the resulting position size fits within available margin at your preferred leverage. Run the numbers through our <a href=\"/liquidation-calculator/\">liquidation calculator</a> to confirm you have adequate buffer. If it exceeds 3–5× your calculated minimum viable position, reconsider the trade size."
